---
import Layout from '../../components/Layout.astro';
const BASE = __BASE_PATH__;
---

<Layout title="自然奇观" currentNav="nature">
  <div class="breadcrumb"><a href={`${BASE}home/`} target="_blank">首页</a><span>›</span>自然奇观</div>
  <h2>🌋 自然奇观</h2>
  <p class="text-muted">大自然鬼斧神工的杰作。收录全国范围内的独特地质景观、罕见自然现象和生态秘境。</p>
  <hr />
  <div class="post-item">
    <span class="tag tag-nature">地质</span>
    <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);"><strong>张掖丹霞地貌全景指南</strong></span>
    <span class="text-muted">甘肃·张掖 | 征稿中</span>
  </div>
  <div class="post-item">
    <span class="tag tag-nature">水文</span>
    <span style="color: var(--color-text-secondary);"><strong>黄果树瀑布群探秘路线</strong></span>
    <span class="text-muted">贵州·安顺 | 征稿中</span>
  </div>
  <p class="text-muted mt-2">本板块刚刚上线，内容持续补充中。</p>
</Layout>
